Package telecom.server

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    LeakyBucketSocket
    Wrapper class that encapsulates leaky bucket function into socket, activates as a worker thread.
    MultiThreadedServer
    Main server class which listens to the port and initiates new worker threads to send data to client.
    ServerReceiverWorker
    Receiver thread to receive command from client and calls back to the specific server thread that initiated it.
